nombre: Island-Style Home on Coffee Farm, 30+Days Only
descripción:
This unique home has style all its own.
2 bdr/2 bath. 30day+ rental
It is island-style: two dwellings, side-by-side, connected by a grassy courtyard. Each dwelling is its own private 1bdr/1bath.

The main house includes large screened-in living room, dining room and full kitchen.

It is situated on a private coffee and fruit farm just 5 minutes from Kealakekua Bay and 10 minutes to the closest grocery stores, restaurants and hospital (KCH).

Perfect for a couple, small family, or 2 couples.

Kick back & relax in this calm, stylish, 2nd-floor space just in Kahana, close to Napili Bay and Kaanapali beach. This private hideaway has wood floors, a large master bedroom, and extra hideaway beds for the living area.

The condo is across the low beach road from the area’s best stretches of sand. The island's best secret snorkel spots and views of Hawaiian green sea turtles ("honu") are a short walk away.

No stress – get into the Aloha spirit and feel free to ask any questions.
